data.description: Welcome to your new home near Camp Lejeune! This charming single family home offers comfort and convenience with 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, granite countertops, recessed lighting and a host of desirable features. Step into luxury with a walk-in shower and sleek tile flooring that complements the modern design. The interior also includes freshly painted walls as well as new carpet in the master bedroom for added comfort. The HVAC system and water heater have been recently replaced, ensuring efficient and reliable operation. The attached garage comes with a freshly epoxied floor, adding durability and aesthetic appeal.Enjoy the benefits of no city taxes while being just a stone's throw away from Camp Lejeune and nearby shopping. Whether it's a quick trip for essentials or a leisurely browse through local stores, everything is within easy reach.Outside, the fenced-in backyard provides a private oasis for relaxation or gatherings with loved ones. Let your furry friends roam freely or create your own outdoor retreat in this tranquil space.Don't miss out on this opportunity to own a home that checks all the boxes for comfort, convenience, and value. The seller is also willing to assist with buyer closing costs or credit for additional improvements making this an even more attractive opportunity for you. Schedule a showing today and make this your new haven!
